title: Halo Infinite Gameplay Updates Livestream - IGN Live

media:group.media:title: Halo Infinite Gameplay Updates Livestream - IGN Live
media:group.media:description:
Join IGN's Stella Chung as we sit down with 343 to discuss all the updates that are coming to Halo Infinie this holiday season. We'll be taking a look at some brand new multiplayer maps, a new capture the flag variant mode called Covert One Flag, as well as taking a closer look at what fans can expect when jumping into the highly anticipated campaign co-op mode.

http://Trolli.com/Halo has a full breakdown of the details where consumers can find the full terms and conditions.

Presented by Trolli.
